  "title": "Quality Inspector (Logistics / Aviation / Aerospace)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Industry: Freight Forwarding / Logistics</strong></p><p><strong>MNC Environment</strong></p><p><strong>Permanent role (AWS Guaranteed + Variable Bonusn + Overtime)</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Inspect aircraft spares</li><li>Verify aircraft spares to ensure appropriate accompanying documents from the OEMs, vendors and suppliers</li><li>Work on continuous improvement projects to improve work areas & procedures</li><li>Facilitate periodic audits from civil aviation authorities & customers</li><li>Maintain Shelf Life records for aircraft spares with limited life</li><li>Monitor and conduct surveillance audits on all stores activities within the Bonded Stores</li><li>Raise Discrepancy Reports for any discrepancies found on any aircraft spares in the Bonded Stores</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Work experience in the aviation industry would be an advantage</li><li>Excellent interpersonal & influencing skills</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office & presentation skills</li></ul><p><strong>Job ID: </strong>QX96WW7Y</p><p><br /></p><p><em><strong>All Successful candidates can expect a very competitive remuneration package and a comprehensive range of benefits.</strong></em></p><p>Kindly email your resume in a detailed <u><strong>Word format</strong></u> to <a href=\"mailto:carlo@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">carlo@peopleprofilers.com</a></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>People Profilers Pte Ltd</strong></p><p>20 Cecil Street, #08-09 PLUS Building Singapore 049705</p><p>+65 6950 9747</p><p><br /></p><p>EA Licence Number: 02C4944</p><p>Registration Number: R1100011</p><p>EA Personnel: Carlo Antonio Dela Cruz</p>",
